1
00:00:06,150 --> 00:00:09,420
♪By the small window♪

2
00:00:10,070 --> 00:00:13,260
♪She is grooming herself♪

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:19,860
♪A fleeting dream at night
brings me back home♪

4
00:00:20,100 --> 00:00:22,180
♪Through willows glows the sinking sun♪

5
00:00:22,300 --> 00:00:23,980
♪Over walls so still and bare♪

6
00:00:24,140 --> 00:00:26,900
♪A few faint strokes remain,
shadows of words♪

7
00:00:27,100 --> 00:00:33,500
♪In my twilight years,
I yearn for what is lost♪

8
00:00:33,540 --> 00:00:36,420
♪I try not to remember♪

9
00:00:36,460 --> 00:00:40,620
♪How far we were apart♪

10
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:47,620
♪But forgetting is hard, with nowhere
to talk my cold thoughts out♪

11
00:00:47,860 --> 00:00:54,740
♪We looked at each other, silent,
lines of tears coursing down♪

12
00:00:54,860 --> 00:00:59,100
♪Now I gaze alone at the full moon,
entranced by its wistful beauty♪

13
00:00:59,100 --> 00:01:02,980
[Agarwood Like a Dream]

14
00:01:03,140 --> 00:01:07,180
[Episode 14]

15
00:01:17,060 --> 00:01:17,860
Buhan.

16
00:01:20,180 --> 00:01:21,540
Who said you could come into this room?

17
00:01:22,620 --> 00:01:24,260
I am your wife,

18
00:01:24,700 --> 00:01:26,460
and that's all I want to be.

19
00:01:27,140 --> 00:01:27,900
Buhan,

20
00:01:28,820 --> 00:01:30,300
I don't want to divorce you.

21
00:01:31,100 --> 00:01:31,900
Buhan,

22
00:01:32,540 --> 00:01:33,900
Grandmother's birthday is approaching,

23
00:01:33,900 --> 00:01:35,740
and I haven't prepared
her birthday gift yet.

24
00:01:36,580 --> 00:01:38,380
Would you accompany me
on a shopping trip?

25
00:01:54,900 --> 00:01:55,700
Buhan,

26
00:01:57,380 --> 00:02:00,220
how about gifting this jade ruyi
to Grandmother as her birthday present?

27
00:02:01,940 --> 00:02:02,780
We'll take this one.

28
00:02:02,860 --> 00:02:03,820
Wrap it up and send it to Ye's Mansion.

29
00:02:04,100 --> 00:02:04,900
Sure.

30
00:02:14,300 --> 00:02:15,100
Buhan,

31
00:02:15,380 --> 00:02:15,780
look.

32
00:02:16,380 --> 00:02:17,740
Do I look good wearing this?

33
00:02:19,180 --> 00:02:20,180
As long as you like it.

34
00:02:21,020 --> 00:02:22,060
From childhood to now,

35
00:02:22,860 --> 00:02:25,220
this is the first time
Buhan has ever given me a gift.

36
00:02:32,900 --> 00:02:33,660
Buhan,

37
00:02:34,060 --> 00:02:35,340
wait for me.

38
00:02:47,260 --> 00:02:49,820
Thank you, Mr. Nan Qing,
for taking me out for a stroll.

39
00:02:50,540 --> 00:02:51,100
It's my pleasure.

40
00:02:51,660 --> 00:02:52,820
Did you like the flowers

41
00:02:52,820 --> 00:02:53,660
I gave you the other day?

42
00:03:01,020 --> 00:03:01,820
It's raining.

43
00:03:01,820 --> 00:03:02,940
Hurry, let's go inside.

44
00:03:09,580 --> 00:03:10,380
Careful.

45
00:03:18,580 --> 00:03:19,380
Are you all right?

46
00:03:21,060 --> 00:03:21,860
Don't move.

47
00:03:35,540 --> 00:03:36,740
Mr. Nan Qing,

48
00:03:39,460 --> 00:03:40,820
are you also here to enjoy the scenery?

49
00:03:41,580 --> 00:03:44,020
I'm out with Miss Rumeng for a stroll.

50
00:03:45,860 --> 00:03:49,140
It's rare to see
Mr. Ye accompanying you.

51
00:03:50,180 --> 00:03:51,660
Grandmother's birthday is approaching.

52
00:03:52,060 --> 00:03:54,980
Buhan and I came out
to pick a gift for her.

53
00:03:55,100 --> 00:03:58,300
He also chose a present for me.

54
00:04:03,700 --> 00:04:05,460
Mr. Ye, you are truly lucky

55
00:04:05,860 --> 00:04:08,860
to have a wife like Ms. Bai,
who's so cultured and well-mannered.

56
00:04:08,860 --> 00:04:10,180
No wonder everyone says

57
00:04:10,940 --> 00:04:12,540
you two are the perfect match.

58
00:04:16,140 --> 00:04:16,980
Mr. Ye,

59
00:04:18,540 --> 00:04:19,820
don't forget the divorce agreement.

60
00:04:30,340 --> 00:04:32,660
The core ingredients in the Night Spirit
are sandalwood and frankincense,

61
00:04:33,060 --> 00:04:35,020
but the selection
of other fragrance materials

62
00:04:35,100 --> 00:04:35,980
must also follow the principles of sovereign,

63
00:04:35,980 --> 00:04:37,020
ministers, assistants, and couriers.

64
00:04:37,100 --> 00:04:37,900
Mhm.

65
00:04:39,780 --> 00:04:40,940
I have come to deliver
the divorce agreement.

66
00:04:44,300 --> 00:04:46,300
Mr. Ye prefers we don't meet too often.

67
00:04:46,300 --> 00:04:47,460
I'll wait in the back,

68
00:04:47,580 --> 00:04:48,140
or else

69
00:04:48,140 --> 00:04:50,500
he might make things hard for you again.

70
00:04:50,540 --> 00:04:51,340
All right.

71
00:04:51,620 --> 00:04:53,380
I have nothing to say to him,

72
00:04:53,380 --> 00:04:54,580
it'll be over soon.

73
00:05:19,380 --> 00:05:20,500
The autumn breeze is chilly,

74
00:05:21,380 --> 00:05:22,780
and this bamboo curtain is a bit old.

75
00:05:23,260 --> 00:05:24,900
I'll find someone
to replace it for you tomorrow.

76
00:05:24,900 --> 00:05:26,300
I can manage it myself,

77
00:05:26,340 --> 00:05:27,660
so no need for you to worry.

78
00:05:29,740 --> 00:05:31,100
It's no big deal.

79
00:05:31,860 --> 00:05:32,900
I'm happy to help.

80
00:05:33,020 --> 00:05:34,780
Aren't you here to deliver
the divorce agreement?

81
00:05:35,580 --> 00:05:36,380
Give it to me.

82
00:05:37,300 --> 00:05:38,100
Sit down.

83
00:05:43,780 --> 00:05:44,860
How can you sign it
if you're not seated?

84
00:05:56,500 --> 00:05:57,900
[Divorce Agreement]

85
00:06:09,020 --> 00:06:11,310
[Signatory]

86
00:06:31,310 --> 00:06:32,740
[Ying Hemeng]

87
00:06:52,860 --> 00:06:54,180
It's all settled between us.

88
00:06:54,220 --> 00:06:55,500
You may leave after signing it.

89
00:07:12,700 --> 00:07:13,700
I'll sign it,

90
00:07:14,060 --> 00:07:15,500
but you need to agree
to a few conditions first.

91
00:07:18,100 --> 00:07:18,860
What are the conditions?

92
00:07:19,100 --> 00:07:20,140
After the divorce,

93
00:07:20,140 --> 00:07:21,660
you will stay at the Qixiang Pavilion

94
00:07:21,660 --> 00:07:23,500
as an incense maker.

95
00:07:23,820 --> 00:07:25,380
Shangjing is such a big city.

96
00:07:25,660 --> 00:07:28,100
Why do I have to make incense
for Qixiang Pavilion?

97
00:07:28,500 --> 00:07:29,380
It's impossible.

98
00:07:30,060 --> 00:07:30,900
What's the second condition?

99
00:07:32,140 --> 00:07:33,980
I don't like this Mr. Nan Qing,

100
00:07:34,660 --> 00:07:36,180
and I won't allow you to marry him.

101
00:07:37,780 --> 00:07:39,260
Who I marry

102
00:07:39,860 --> 00:07:41,100
is none of your concern.

103
00:07:43,140 --> 00:07:44,500
Since you don't agree,

104
00:07:45,340 --> 00:07:47,260
I won't sign it.

105
00:07:51,860 --> 00:07:54,860
Miss Rumeng
is determined to divorce you.

106
00:07:55,460 --> 00:07:56,740
So why keep pestering her?

107
00:07:57,220 --> 00:07:58,180
Mr. Ye,

108
00:07:59,500 --> 00:08:00,300
please.

109
00:08:03,820 --> 00:08:05,540
As long as the agreement isn't signed,

110
00:08:06,700 --> 00:08:08,340
you will still be my wife.

111
00:08:25,620 --> 00:08:26,900
Please, Mr. Ye, mind your manners.

112
00:08:27,500 --> 00:08:29,580
I am no longer your wife.

113
00:08:30,540 --> 00:08:31,940
I'm here to get the divorce agreement.

114
00:08:33,460 --> 00:08:34,260
Meng,

115
00:08:34,860 --> 00:08:35,980
you're finally back.

116
00:08:36,580 --> 00:08:37,780
After all this time,

117
00:08:38,100 --> 00:08:39,540
if it weren't for others
not knowing about the matter,

118
00:08:39,540 --> 00:08:40,940
Grandmother
would never have let you off.

119
00:08:42,340 --> 00:08:44,140
We agreed
to find the true culprit together.

120
00:08:44,980 --> 00:08:46,340
Are you going to give up now?

121
00:08:47,700 --> 00:08:48,780
The truth of the past

122
00:08:48,940 --> 00:08:50,340
and my current freedom

123
00:08:50,340 --> 00:08:51,700
are both crucial to me.

124
00:08:52,260 --> 00:08:52,940
Anyway,

125
00:08:53,580 --> 00:08:55,580
I will never be your wife.

126
00:08:55,860 --> 00:08:56,900
Thanks

127
00:08:56,900 --> 00:08:59,540
to the medicinal incense
from Qixiang Pavilion over the years,

128
00:08:59,780 --> 00:09:02,700
my husband's health
has significantly improved.

129
00:09:03,100 --> 00:09:05,580
The imperial physician
has changed his prescription,

130
00:09:05,580 --> 00:09:06,980
and while the medicinal incense
is supplemental,

131
00:09:06,980 --> 00:09:08,060
it must be adjusted accordingly

132
00:09:08,060 --> 00:09:10,140
to prevent any adverse reactions
with the new medicine.

133
00:09:10,260 --> 00:09:11,780
Incense and medicine have shared roots
since ancient times.

134
00:09:11,780 --> 00:09:13,580
It is an honor for Qixiang Pavilion

135
00:09:13,580 --> 00:09:15,540
to assist Your Highness.

136
00:09:16,740 --> 00:09:20,140
You are Ms. Chen, the one who made
incense for me last time, right?

137
00:09:22,860 --> 00:09:25,260
Then let's leave it to her this time.

138
00:09:26,300 --> 00:09:28,060
I am honored, Your Highness.

139
00:09:28,260 --> 00:09:29,860
But I'm inexperienced

140
00:09:29,980 --> 00:09:32,540
and not well-versed
in the properties of medicinal herbs,

141
00:09:32,900 --> 00:09:33,780
so I'm afraid...

142
00:09:33,780 --> 00:09:35,100
Don't worry.

143
00:09:35,100 --> 00:09:36,780
All you need to do

144
00:09:36,780 --> 00:09:38,580
is follow
the imperial physician's prescription.

145
00:09:38,940 --> 00:09:40,180
Your Highness,

146
00:09:40,540 --> 00:09:41,660
I no longer

147
00:09:42,020 --> 00:09:43,780
make incense for Qixiang Pavilion.

148
00:09:43,780 --> 00:09:45,740
Her Highness thinks so highly of you.

149
00:09:45,740 --> 00:09:47,540
You should thank her now

150
00:09:47,740 --> 00:09:49,420
and make incense for Qixiang Pavilion.

151
00:09:49,780 --> 00:09:52,220
All the ingredients in the warehouse
will be at your disposal.

152
00:09:52,220 --> 00:09:53,980
What more
could you possibly complain about?

153
00:09:54,060 --> 00:09:55,300
If anything is lacking,

154
00:09:55,620 --> 00:09:57,780
the Bai family from Pinggu
will take care of it.

155
00:09:58,100 --> 00:09:58,900
The Bai family?

156
00:09:58,900 --> 00:10:00,740
It's the perfect opportunity

157
00:10:00,740 --> 00:10:02,140
to gather some information from them.

158
00:10:02,740 --> 00:10:04,140
Thank you, Grandmother,
for your instructions.

159
00:10:04,260 --> 00:10:05,820
It is such a privilege for me

160
00:10:05,820 --> 00:10:07,260
to make incense for Lord Wen.

161
00:10:07,300 --> 00:10:09,060
I will not let Your Highness down.

162
00:10:10,100 --> 00:10:11,260
Your Highness,

163
00:10:11,260 --> 00:10:12,500
let's have some tea inside.

164
00:10:21,620 --> 00:10:23,020
You said that just now because...

165
00:10:23,100 --> 00:10:24,180
After we finish making the incense,

166
00:10:24,580 --> 00:10:25,700
we will divorce.

167
00:10:26,940 --> 00:10:28,260
That day at the pavilion,

168
00:10:29,340 --> 00:10:30,780
you said that pastries are fragile,

169
00:10:31,500 --> 00:10:33,500
just like the beautiful things in life.

170
00:10:35,460 --> 00:10:38,060
So, you've long decided
to leave me, haven't you?

171
00:10:38,740 --> 00:10:40,620
Every moment I'm with you,

172
00:10:41,180 --> 00:10:42,380
I just want to kill you.

173
00:10:45,340 --> 00:10:47,060
I won't allow you to marry Nan Qing.

174
00:10:47,460 --> 00:10:48,220
You won't allow it?

175
00:10:48,860 --> 00:10:50,060
Who are you to say that?

176
00:10:50,860 --> 00:10:52,180
If it hadn't been for the grudge
of the past,

177
00:10:52,180 --> 00:10:53,700
I would never have married you.

178
00:10:54,900 --> 00:10:55,980
You're not like him.

179
00:10:56,540 --> 00:10:57,980
I trust

180
00:10:58,220 --> 00:10:59,380
and love him.

181
00:10:59,700 --> 00:11:02,100
I may have had
feelings for him long ago.

182
00:11:02,500 --> 00:11:03,940
If it weren't for revenge,

183
00:11:05,220 --> 00:11:05,820
it would have been him and me

184
00:11:06,540 --> 00:11:09,340
falling in love
during the incense competition.

185
00:11:28,660 --> 00:11:29,420
Very well.

186
00:11:31,100 --> 00:11:32,380
Then, Miss Ying,

187
00:11:33,060 --> 00:11:35,380
please make the last batch of incense
for Qixiang Pavilion.

188
00:11:36,420 --> 00:11:37,220
After that,

189
00:11:38,940 --> 00:11:40,820
you will no longer be my wife.

190
00:11:43,420 --> 00:11:45,900
Please remember what you said today.

191
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:34,620
♪Familiar yet strange sights♪

192
00:12:35,110 --> 00:12:37,540
♪The tale's first light♪

193
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:39,910
♪Growing with time's flow♪

194
00:12:40,310 --> 00:12:43,450
♪Somber and mournful grief♪

195
00:12:43,860 --> 00:12:46,740
♪The final act, my swan song as a bait♪

196
00:12:47,030 --> 00:12:49,780
♪Has freed the heart from all desires♪

197
00:12:50,460 --> 00:12:54,780
♪As I dance with wolves,
love lies hidden deep♪

198
00:12:57,100 --> 00:13:01,660
♪The scented sachet,
a memory that never fades♪

199
00:13:02,420 --> 00:13:06,860
♪With every passing day,
our love simmers and ignites♪

200
00:13:08,140 --> 00:13:11,020
♪The ache born
from our ephemeral meetings♪

201
00:13:11,620 --> 00:13:14,420
♪Etched upon the canvas of my heart♪

202
00:13:15,060 --> 00:13:19,460
♪How to untangle
this lasting, aching desire♪

203
00:13:21,340 --> 00:13:23,820
♪In the face of such a bewitching gaze?♪

204
00:13:24,700 --> 00:13:30,220
♪Soft melodies caress locked windows,
reaching out to the setting sun♪

205
00:13:31,140 --> 00:13:33,660
♪Gently adorning with twilight's charm♪

206
00:13:34,020 --> 00:13:36,660
♪My remaining breaths,
the thoughts that they bear♪

207
00:13:37,180 --> 00:13:41,660
♪The vision of you,
the one that fills my mind♪
